snippet.title: Mortal Online 2 - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Craft your own unique story in the worlds most immersive sandbox MMORPG. 

Mortal Online 2 is a next generation, first-person, persistent sandbox MMORPG set in a fantasy world with a focus on immersion and deep game systems, where your individual reputation matters. 

Who will you be? 

Pre-Order now at https://www.mortalonline2.com/shop/
